<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFAppenzeller2004">Appenzeller, Tim (2004). "<a href="http://magma.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0402/feature5/index.html" class="external text" title="http://magma.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0402/feature5/index.html" rel="nofollow">The case of the missing carbon</a>". <i>National Geographic Magazine</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://magma.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0402/feature5/index.html" class="external free" title="http://magma.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0402/feature5/index.html" rel="nofollow">http://magma.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0402/feature5/index.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+case+of+the+missing+carbon&amp;rft.jtitle=National+Geographic+Magazine&amp;rft.aulast=Appenzeller&amp;rft.aufirst=Tim&amp;rft.au=Appenzeller%2C+Tim&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmagma.nationalgeographic.com%2Fngm%2F0402%2Ffeature5%2Findex.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Carbon_cycle"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> - article about the missing carbon sink</li>
